.TH CONV-BOOT 1 "July 2026" "ConVigurator Manual"
.SH NAME
conv-boot \- ConVigurator Boot Configuration Tuner for hardware and filesystem service scaling.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B conv-boot
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B conv-boot
is executed automatically on system startup via conv-boot.service. It audits hardware characteristics (such as the presence of touchscreens via udev metadata) and filesystem layouts (verifying if root / is hosted on a Btrfs subvolume or a Live USB overlayfs mount) to toggle and scale corresponding services (e.g., evdev-rce.service and snapper-cleanup).
.SH SEE ALSO
conv-build(1), conv-alias(1)
